```r

#> 
#> Attaching package: 'dplyr'

#> The following objects are masked from 'package:stats':

library(kthapi)

departments <- 
  altmetric_explorer %>% 
  select(-altmetric_id) %>%
  mutate(link = sprintf("<a href='%s' title='%s'>%s</a>", href, level, desc)) %>%
  select(`Altmetric URL` = link, `DiVA Unit` = diva_id, Count = count)
```
